title: Americana Album Art
description:
The album American by the Offspring has some really great art in the booklet for every song, which is pretty nice. I scanned each page and saved it in the PNG (lossless) format. They&#039;re pretty high quality innately and I feel I&#039;ve preserved them in a digital format that suits them. 

*Note* Some of the text looks kind of screwy and slanted, IT&#039;S SUPPOSED TO BE THAT WAY, just to let you know.
